{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/shambala-roerich/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"99cb7056-1e2f-543d-8b40-d70b89c79ab6","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0c187c242ae62c6be8486e9bf4b1bb75/18e3b/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/0c187c242ae62c6be8486e9bf4b1bb75/18e3b/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0c187c242ae62c6be8486e9bf4b1bb75/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/0c187c242ae62c6be8486e9bf4b1bb75/18e3b/1.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>At some point, while working in Webmarket, I was contacted by Leonardo Olazabal, the founder of the Shambala Roerich museum in Bedia, Bizkaia.</p>\n<p>He needed help with the maintenance of the museum’s website, which at that point, was using Joomla. I helped him with a few changes and we decided to build a new template with more features, like video player, better blogs taxonomy, etc:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b57206e73f9eaf49cda644d44266deda/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/b57206e73f9eaf49cda644d44266deda/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b57206e73f9eaf49cda644d44266deda/d1f95/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/b57206e73f9eaf49cda644d44266deda/dbdff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>A year later, we decided to build a responsive website using Wordpress and implement an e-commerce module to sell his books.</p>\n<p>I am also very grateful to Leonardo and his wife Petri for having supported my <a href=\"/samurai-route\">Samurai Route</a> trip with their sponsorship.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2009"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Shambala Roerich","categories":"web ux design wordpress joomla","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/41c7394edecd4a28e7c4d71294c42ac9/f3583/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/shambala-roerich/","source":"work"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}